"""The {{ cli_name }} command: a delivery adapter around the core *and* the repo's
task runner and control plane (so there is no Makefile to maintain across
platforms).

Command groups:
  {{ cli_name }} project …   manage projects (core adapter)
  {{ cli_name }} note …      manage notes (core adapter)
  {{ cli_name }} db …        database migrations (Alembic)
  {{ cli_name }} build …     build artifacts
  {{ cli_name }} license …   license status/install + vendor keygen/issue
plus dev / desktop / doctor / info / test / lint / fmt / openapi / gen / version.
"""

